    "Liu et al. [234] studied distributed interference management for ISAC networks, where each ISAC-BS was equipped with an independent neural network to manage interference.",
    "The achievable communication rate was maximized, subject to the power and sensing constraints, through joint beamforming and power allocation optimization.",
    "In addition, the USL and TL were used for power allocation and beamforming optimization, respectively.",
    "System-level designTraditional ISAC systems follow the modular paradigm, and the entire system can be divided into several independent blocks, such as the transmitter and receiver, to be optimized respectively.",
